'''湯馬士·安祖·"湯姆"·赫度史東'''（'''Thomas Andrew "Tom" Huddlestone'''，{{bd|1986年|12月28日|catIdx=Huddlestone, Tom}}），出生於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[東米德蘭茲|東米德蘭茲]][[諾丁漢郡|諾丁漢郡]][[诺丁汉|诺丁汉]]，是一名職業足球員，現時效力[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]球隊[[赫尔城足球俱乐部|赫尔城]]。

==球隊==
赫度史東出身[[德比郡足球俱乐部|打比郡]]青訓學院（Derby County's Academy），年僅16歲，即在2003/04年球季開季首場對[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]的比賽處子登場，結果以0-3落敗<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3113043.stm |title=Derby 0-3 Stoke |access-date=2008-08-01 |archive-date=2020-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200627105607/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/3113043.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2004年2月剛滿17歲的赫度史東簽署首份職業合約，年期兩年半是18歲以下球員可簽署最長的年期，直到2006年夏季<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/derby_county/3490974.stm |title=New deal for teen starlet |access-date=2008-08-01 |archive-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003044819/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/derby_county/3490974.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2005年1月赫度史東簽約加盟[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|熱刺]]，據報轉會費最高可達到250萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/t/tottenham_hotspur/4227853.stm |title=Spurs agree deal for Huddlestone |accessdate=2008-08-01 |archive-date=2018-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180621045716/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/t/tottenham_hotspur/4227853.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，可留效打比郡直到球季結束以協助球隊打升班戰<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/derby_county/4229177.stm |title=Huddlestone aims for winning exit |access-date=2008-08-01 |archive-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003043530/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/d/derby_county/4229177.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。打比郡獲得第四位參加季後升級附加賽<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/4500769.stm |title=Derby 3-1 Preston |access-date=2008-08-01 |archive-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003043654/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/4500769.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但不幸兩回合累計0-2負於[[普雷斯顿足球俱乐部|普雷斯頓]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/4537183.stm |title=Derby 0-0 Preston (agg 0-2) |access-date=2008-08-01 |archive-date=2021-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211222453/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/4537183.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2005/06年球季赫度史東未為熱刺上陣前先獲外借到[[伍尔弗汉普顿流浪足球俱乐部|狼隊]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/4374622.stm |title=Huddlestone joins Wolves on loan |access-date=2008-08-01 |archive-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003043707/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wolverhampton_wanderers/4374622.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，期間在對母會打比郡時取得首個聯賽入球<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/4430984.stm |title=Derby 0-3 Wolves |accessdate=2008-08-01 |archive-date=2017-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170903172338/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/4430984.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。稍後返回熱刺，於2006年1月31日作客對[[富勒姆足球俱乐部|富咸]]時首次披上熱刺球衣，替補上場，以0-1落敗。赫度史東在2006年9月14日作客[[布拉格斯拉维亚足球俱乐部|布拉格斯拉维亚]]（Slavia Prague）的[[歐洲足協盃|歐洲足協盃]]首次正選上陣，以1-0獲得勝利。同年11月8日[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]第四圈對[[韦尔港足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:韦尔港;zh-hk:維爾港}-]]赫度史東首度為熱刺入球，更梅開二度，他在加時的第二個入球將熱刺帶入半準決賽<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/6116418.stm |title=Tottenham 3-1 Port Vale (aet) |access-date=2008-08-01 |archive-date=2007-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070307104832/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/league_cup/6116418.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。12月17日對[[曼城足球俱乐部|曼城]]時射入首個效力熱刺的聯賽入球，赫度史東首先憑自由球助攻先開紀錄，再於24分鐘以一球精彩的半「窩利」將比數改寫成2-0，最終以2-1擊敗對手<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/6164455.stm |title=Man City 1 - 2 Tottenham |access-date=2008-08-01 |archive-date=2020-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200112202434/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/6164455.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2006年12月25日赫度史東加簽四年半新約，留隊直到2011年<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/t/tottenham_hotspur/6211123.stm |title=Huddlestone agrees new Spurs deal |access-date=2008-08-01 |archive-date=2019-04-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190409145517/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/t/tottenham_hotspur/6211123.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，更於2008年6月30日簽署五年改善條件的新約，效力熱刺直到2013年<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.tottenhamhotspur.com/news/articles/newdealfortom300608.html |title=New deal for Tom |accessdate=2008-08-01 |archive-date=2011-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111110202051/http://www.tottenhamhotspur.com/news/articles/newdealfortom300608.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由於赫度史東在2009-2010賽季發揮出色，截至3月15日為止替球隊上陣34場攻入3球，並累積為熱刺披甲147場，2010年3月15日熱刺在球會官方網站宣佈再與赫度史東續約至2015年。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.tottenhamhotspur.com/news/articles/tompensnewdeal150310.html |title=Tom pens new deal |access-date=2010-03-20 |archive-date=2010-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100322191828/http://www.tottenhamhotspur.com/news/articles/tompensnewdeal150310.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==國家隊==
赫度史東是[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U-21]]的主力成員，2007年6月5日對斯洛伐克U-21大勝5-0中取得首個國際賽入球<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6725139.stm |title=England U21 5-0 Slovakia U21 |access-date=2008-08-01 |archive-date=2021-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210610105606/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6725139.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[2007年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|2007年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽]]決賽週赫度史東在兩場分組賽中上陣，首場正選上場與捷克U-21賽和0-0<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6738781.stm |title=Czech Rep U21 0-0 England U21 |access-date=2008-08-01 |archive-date=2007-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070909122225/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6738781.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>；分組賽最後一場對塞爾維亞U-21，已領先2-0及穩奪分組第二名出線權的英格蘭在88分鐘調入赫度史東加強防守，落場僅兩分鐘，在防守對方自由球時被球證[[紅牌|紅牌]]直接驅逐離場<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6759921.stm |title=England U21 2-0 Serbia U21 |access-date=2008-08-01 |archive-date=2019-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130170500/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6759921.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，赫度史東停賽兩場<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6764825.stm |title=FA makes Huddlestone ban appeal |access-date=2008-08-01 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128032751/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6764825.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，錯過準決賽對主辦國荷蘭U-21的大戰。

2007年9月11日作客2-0擊敗保加利亞U-21時赫度史東再度入球<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6988587.stm |title=Bulgaria U21 0-2 England U21 |access-date=2008-08-01 |archive-date=2019-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190701175728/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6988587.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2008年5月15日作客友賽威爾斯U-21作為慶祝威爾斯U-21第100場比賽中，赫度史東於19分鐘射入十二碼先開紀錄，最終2-0獲勝<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7365340.stm |title=Wales U21 0-2 England U21 |access-date=2008-08-01 |archive-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003043422/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7365340.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2008年5月赫度史東獲[[法比奥·卡佩罗|卡比路]]徵召，加入美洲之旅的31人大國腳名單之中<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7395247.stm |title=Hart & Jagielka in England squad |access-date=2008-08-01 |archive-date=2020-08-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200801163235/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7395247.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在對[[美國國家足球隊|美國]]及[[千里達及托巴哥國家足球隊|千里達及托巴哥]]兩場比賽中作未有上場的替補球員。

2008年10月14日[[2009年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|2009年歐洲U-21足球錦標賽]]外圍附加賽次回合對[[威爾斯21歲以下足球代表隊|威爾斯U-21]]是赫度史東第30次代表英格蘭U-21上陣，他在13分鐘憑禁區邊緣的[[自由球|自由球]]為球隊先開紀錄；但下半場66分鐘因一次遲落腳的攔截而被罰[[紅牌|紅牌]]離場。幸好英格蘭U-21仍能力保2-2的紀錄，兩回合累計5-4晉級決賽週<ref>BBC Sports：[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7665226.stm {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7665226.stm |date=20201109013424 }} {{en}}England U21 2-2 Wales U21 (5-4)]</ref>。

2009年11月8日首度獲[[卡比路|卡比路]]徵召入[[友誼賽|友賽]][[巴西國家足球隊|巴西]]的[[英格蘭足球代表隊|大國腳]]的名單中<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8349681.stm |title=Striker Bent gets England call-up |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-11-08 |accessdate=2009-11-09 |archive-date=2018-10-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181003045127/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8349681.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，獲派後補上陣作處子秀<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8353751.stm |title=Brazil 1-0 England |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-11-14 |accessdate=2009-11-16 |archive-date=2020-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122020244/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8353751.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

